{"tid":1537281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不麻木，由生活做起] 戴口罩，直到贏","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:14:48.000Z","uid":63285,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ba5e302506c2a0e4deaa77be3db23fbbc26c22","tid":1537281,"uid":63285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:10:32.000Z","msg":"警暴每一晚都係度發生<br />\n大家唔應該只係係度鬧<br />\n反之係要企出黎表態<br />\n對抗白色恐怖<br />\n罷工你唔敢<br />\n跳閘又驚犯法<br />\n黑衫又話唔夠衫<br />\n戴番個口罩你又肯唔肯? <br />\n<br />\n記住，一切由生活做起，會變成習慣。<br />\n<br />\n不自由，毋寧死<br />\n戴口罩，直至贏<br />\n<br />\n口罩，係自由，係權利。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xz1WvDO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxz1WvDO.gif&h=336c4718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsMrSRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsMrSRF.jpg&h=f9b10732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mk17Cim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmk17Cim.png&h=ba403c8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncredit: 8.18文宣努力<br />\n<br />\n由聽日起，全民戴口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534721\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534721</a>"},{"pid":"7e99108822805ef35cfd3c778b55ef5c2211b89b","tid":1537281,"uid":63285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:12:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"532641690559f681e79d394860fa4ec65032b233","tid":1537281,"uid":63285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"802c22ccf910a1c0592a878027a6f819fe9fa751","tid":1537281,"uid":63285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab8737051ac7a102a381f0bbb8755906ad552b15","tid":1537281,"uid":63285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b36a90a20b5cb1d07daf7653a49532e417389e56","tid":1537281,"uid":63285,"like":0,"